1
00:00:05,360 --> 00:00:07,759
[SPEAKER_01] Dobrodošli još jedan podcast Budi osnažena.

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] S nama je danas predivna Petra Mikulić.

3
00:00:10,160 --> 00:00:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] Petra, dobrodošla.

4
00:00:11,599 --> 00:00:12,960
